---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-gray mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        NoteDemo collects only the information needed to provide the service:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600">
        <li>Email address (for authentication)</li>
        <li>Name and roll number (for watermarking)</li>
        <li>Device information (for device binding)</li>
        <li>Page access logs (for rate-limiting and analytics)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600">
        <li>To authenticate your identity</li>
        <li>To display your name/roll number as a watermark on content</li>
        <li>To enforce subscription access</li>
        <li>To prevent abuse and unauthorized sharing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">3. Data Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Your data is stored securely in Supabase (PostgreSQL). We do not share your personal data with third parties except as required to operate the service (Cloudinary for image delivery, Razorpay for payment processing).
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">4. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        If you have questions about this policy, please contact the founding team directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
